**Draven is going to be really strong in Season 5
**
**Full build:
**{{item:3508}} {{item:3031}} {{item:3046}} {{item:3078}} {{item:3142}} {{item:3035}} +{{item:2140}} 

Summoners: {{summoner:3}} {{summoner:4}} 

**80% Crit chance:** Nothing to explain here :)
**2000+ Damage from Axe Crits:** (2 hit on any squishy or ADC after his armour reduction etc) It's very possible to one shot ppl if u axe late game and crit + trinity force proc.
**Huge attack speed from items: **ghost active, Frenzy mastery and Draven W. (Tl;Dr you get more than 2 attacks per second & rember u need 2 hits one of them with an axe to kill none-tanky champs. GG in 1 second) Also the more attack speed u have the easier is to catch axes i reckon
**Very tanky:** I was very sad after blood thirst change/it was Draven nerf but now Tanky Draven is back, Crit, Reaver Wrath elixer and health from TF make u very very very tanky late game. 
**Good move speed: **you can spam Ws cos u have Reaver, will never run out of mana. and TF PD and TF passive, no need for boots, also u have Ghostblade for more good measure.




